[Student "S"]
{NORTH's 3\H rebid shows better than average strength and six trumps.

Just what SOUTH was hoping for. She bids Blackwood - her plan is to bid 7\H 
if NORTH has three Aces, bid 6\H if he has two Aces, 
and stop at 5\H if he has just one. If North has no Aces SOUTH will get a new partner.}

