[Student "S"]
{EAST indicates an above normal opening with five \Ss by her 3NT rebid.

WEST also has some extra strength so he makes a Control showing bid of 4\H.

Despite both partners showing extra strength East merely signs of at 4\S. Why? Because WEST's 
Control bid of 4\H denied first-round control in both \Cs and 
\Ds. EAST realized she was off two Aces.}

